<div id="main_content">
	<h2>Call to Action: Ambitious Climate Plan Positions UCF as Regional Sustainability Leader</h2>
	
	<p class="article_info">
		
			By Kimberly Lewis
		
		<span class="date">Feb. 3, 2010</span></p>
	
	
	
		<div class="article_img" style="width: 345px;">

			<img alt="Article Main Picture" src="http://news.ucf.edu/resources/sites/UCF/content/live/NEWS/2000/NE2043/en_US/bike rider and engineering bldg FULL.jpg" height="226" width="345"  /> 
			
				<p class="photo_credit">Photo: Jacque Brund</p>
			
			<p>With 60,000 students, faculty and staff at UCF, each individual effort to conserve energy helps the university achieve climate neutrality.</p>
			
				<p class="note"><a class="full_photo" id="popup.jsp?article_id=002400417c223ec20125ae9931fd001eea">Full Photo</a></p>
			
			
			
			
					
						
						
						
					
			
			
			
					
						
						
						
					
			
			
			
		</div>
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
		
